@startuml
!theme plain

actor User
participant "Popup/Options UI" as UI
participant "Background Script" as BS
participant "Content Script" as CS
database "Precomputed Words Database" as PWD
participant "TTS Module" as TTS

User -> UI : Installs Extension
User -> UI : Opens Popup/Options
UI -> BS : Sends User Settings
BS -> CS : Sends Command to Alter Text
CS -> PWD : Fetches Word Transformations
CS -> TTS : Triggers Text-to-Speech (if needed)
UI -> User : Displays Educational Content (optional)

@enduml
